{"tid":1192071,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PSN日服PS+會員即將漲價，你準備囤貨了嗎？","createTime":"2019-06-08T08:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T09:32:23.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a6695fdab15bce32c192cd7772adf95b9981db","tid":1192071,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"Playstation日服PS+會員服務將從8月1日起價格上漲。1個月會員價格調整至850日元（原價514日元），3個月會員價格調整至2150日元（原價1337日元），而12個月會員價格保持不變，8月1日之後仍舊為5143日元。<br />\n<br />\nSIE官方宣布，香港地區的Playstation Plus會員服務即將迎來價格調整，調整時間從2019年8月1日開始正式實施。<br />\n<br />\n港服的PS+會員服務將從每月38港幣調整為48港幣，三個月會員從原來的88港幣調整為128港幣，12個月會員從原來的268港幣調整為308港幣。已經購買的會員服務不受影響，如果玩家使用了自動續費服務，2019年8月1日當天或之後的付款將以修改後的價格進行收費。<br />\n<br />\n當然這次除了港服之外，日服PSN會員也有一定幅度的漲價。<br />\n<br />\nPSN會員服務除了提供聯機和雲存檔服務之外，最吸引人的就是每月更新會員免費領取的遊戲了。"},{"pid":"a7282c79b49719a110b028ce305bf3a3b8de90c2","tid":1192071,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"好似M記咁,加之前先畀一輪甜頭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851172e3167ac98a5eb67ad0132c15a6d676896d","tid":1192071,"uid":18948,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srodHzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrodHzU.png&h=2b6806e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1911a3b63cbd9cc708f06055b2923f4e9346ce35","tid":1192071,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851172e3167ac98a5eb67ad0132c15a6d676896d","tid":1192071,"uid":18948,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srodHzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrodHzU.png&h=2b6806e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"家陣7折 要瘋狂入貨"},{"pid":"27645769053f250494fada875531dfbd7fb45f8a","tid":1192071,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s